---
import BaseLayout from "@layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About Guy Michaelis.">
  <div class="wrap-narrow">
    <h1 style="margin-top:3rem;">About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm <strong>Guy Michaelis</strong> — a Senior DevOps Engineer based in
      the Tel Aviv area, specializing in cloud infrastructure, Kubernetes, CI/CD,
      and platform engineering at scale.
    </p>
    <p>
      I work through <strong>Tikal</strong>, a hands-on tech consultancy,
      where I embed with client teams to architect, build, and operate production
      systems. Over the years I've worked across a wide range of industries —
      from AI and fintech to healthcare, insurance, and enterprise SaaS —
      with companies like <strong>QbiqAI</strong>, <strong>Zoominfo</strong>,
      <strong>Waterfall</strong>, <strong>Snappy</strong>, <strong>Lynx.md</strong>,
      <strong>SentinelOne</strong>, <strong>ThomsonReuters</strong>,
      <strong>Paypal</strong>, <strong>SAP</strong>, <strong>Sapiens</strong>,
      and more.
    </p>
    <p>
      My day-to-day work spans Kubernetes orchestration, GitOps (ArgoCD, Flux),
      infrastructure-as-code with Terraform, observability stacks (Prometheus,
      Grafana, Loki, Jaeger), and microservices transformation — always with an
      eye for reliability, automation, and developer experience.
    </p>

    <h2>Work with me</h2>
    <div style="margin:2rem 0;padding:1.5em;background:var(--c-theme-light);border:2px solid var(--c-accent);border-radius:var(--radius,4px);text-align:center;">
      <h3 style="margin:0 0 0.5em;">Open for Consulting</h3>
      <p style="margin:0 0 1em;">
        Available through Tikal for consulting engagements, cloud architecture
        reviews, platform engineering, and infrastructure automation projects.
      </p>
      <div style="display:flex;gap:0.8em;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/guy-michaelis-56889/" style="display:inline-block;padding:0.6em 1.4em;border:2px solid var(--c-accent);color:var(--c-accent);border-radius:var(--radius,4px);text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Personal</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a lifelong learner who enjoys diving deep into new technologies,
      automating the mundane, and sharing knowledge with the community. I speak
      Hebrew natively and English fluently.
    </p>

    <h2>This site</h2>
    <p>
      This is my personal blog and portfolio — a collection of thoughts,
      tutorials, and deep dives into DevOps, cloud infrastructure, and platform
      engineering. All opinions are my own.
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
